格鲁伯（John Gruber）和亚伦·斯沃茨（Aaron Swartz）。",{"type":182,"children":183,"toc":282},"root",[184,193,199,204,231,236,241,254,259,277],{"type":185,"tag":186,"props":187,"children":189},"element","h4",{"id":188},"markdown-inline-style",[190],{"type":191,"value":192},"text","Markdown Inline Style",{"type":185,"tag":194,"props":195,"children":196},"p",{},[197],{"type":191,"value":198},"通过 VuePress 可以在 Markdown 文件中嵌套 HTML 和 VueJS 代码，然而贴到掘金之后需要我手动贴图，太麻烦了。",{"type":185,"tag":194,"props":200,"children":201},{},[202],{"type":191,"value":203},"于是我测试了几种 Inline CSS 的方案：",{"type":185,"tag":205,"props":206,"children":207},"ul",{},[208,221],{"type":185,"tag":209,"props":210,"children":211},"li",{},[212],{"type":185,"tag":213,"props":214,"children":218},"a",{"href":215,"rel":216},"https://mdnice.com/",[217],"nofollow",[219],{"type":191,"value":220},"MarkdownNice",{"type":185,"tag":209,"props":222,"children":223},{},[224],{"type":185,"tag":213,"props":225,"children":228},{"href":226,"rel":227},"https://github.com/jonkemp/inline-css",[217],[229],{"type":191,"value":230},"InlineCSS",{"type":185,"tag":194,"props":232,"children":233},{},[234],{"type":191,"value":235},"不过结果都不理想，MarkdownNice 的主题，一点儿也不好康。.. InlineCSS 有很多很多很多问题。..",{"type":185,"tag":194,"props":237,"children":238},{},[239],{"type":191,"value":240},"这两种工具我都放弃了，然后我尝试了组合工具的可能性。",{"type":185,"tag":205,"props":242,"children":243},{},[244,249],{"type":185,"tag":209,"props":245,"children":246},{},[247],{"type":191,"value":248},"先通过 SingleFile 将网页保存为一个整体的 HTML 文件",{"type":185,"tag":209,"props":250,"children":251},{},[252],{"type":191,"value":253},"再使用 InlineCSS + Cheerio 手写代码并规避 InlineCSS 的一些配置问题",{"type":185,"tag":194,"props":255,"children":256},{},[257],{"type":191,"value":258},"虽然期间有很多坑，但从最后尝试的结果来说，总的方向可行。",{"type":185,"tag":205,"props":260,"children":261},{},[262,267,272],{"type":185,"tag":209,"props":263,"children":264},{},[265],{"type":191,"value":266},"SingleFile 会自动内联图片和字体文件，这个好解决，处理之前直接打开控制台修改对应元素避免内联即可，比如将图片的 SRC 属性名改为 SRCBACKUP",{"type":185,"tag":209,"props":268,"children":269},{},[270],{"type":191,"value":271},"InlineCSS 合并时 Margin、MarginBottom 这些重复的属性不会被合并，所以出现了部分样式问题",{"type":185,"tag":209,"props":273,"children":274},{},[275],{"type":191,"value":276},"InlineCSS 解析 CSS 不能解析 CSS 变量",{"type":185,"tag":194,"props":278,"children":279},{},[280],{"type":191,"value":281},"因为相关问题很多，虽然方向可行，但还是弃坑了。最近需要贴文章时还是直接贴 Markdown，懒得再做转换了。以后重新再捡起来的时候，也许会写个直接在浏览器中跑的脚本，毕竟直接调用 DOM API 获取样式的稳定性感觉要比用 InlineCSS 好。",{"title":178,"searchDepth":283,"depth":283,"links":284},2,[],"markdown","content:6.maps:_markdown:markdown.md","content","6.maps/_markdown/markdown.md","6.maps/_markdown/markdown","md",[292,296],{"_path":293,"title":294,"description":295},"/maps/_management/slice/standalone-data-engineering-team","Standalone Data Engineering Teams（独立数据工程团队）","为什么将数据工程从业务领域团队中剥离出来是一种组织反模式，以及应该如何用平台 + 领域团队协作来取代它。",{"_path":297,"title":298,"description":299},"/maps/_medicine/medicine","医疗","常见医疗知识、疾病、药物等。",1771695780076]